name: di

class.name: Injectable
class.preview: Annotation that can be applied to a class for which type factories should be generated to be used by StaticInjector.

class.name: Injectables
class.preview: Annotation that can be applied to the library declaration listing all types for which type factories should be generated to be used by StaticInjector.

class.name: Key
class.preview: Key to which an Injector binds a Provider. This is a pair consisting of a angular/di.Key.type and an optional angular/di.Key.annotation.

class.name: Module
class.preview: Module contributes configuration information to an Injector by providing a collection of type bindings that specify how each type is created.
